The Boston Police Department chases two carjacking suspects in the MIT shooting death of a campus policeman to the nearby suburb of Watertown where, after a gunfight that included explosives, an MBTA officer is injured, one suspect is dead, and the other flees but is later captured. (Boston Herald)The United Nations Human Rights Council authorises an international investigation into alleged war crimes during the Sri Lankan Civil War. (Al Jazeera) (Washington Post) (BBC)